# Facility Registry install
# Source: https://bitbucket.org/instedd/resource_map/wiki/Install%20&%20Update

Set up fully qualified domain name in /etc/hosts
  vim /etc/hosts
    127.0.0.1   fr.example.com  fr
    
Run the setup script  
  curl http://apt.instedd.org/setup.sh | bash
  
Install resource map
  sudo apt-get install resourcemap
  
Point your browser to your domain name / IP to access resource map
